object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	AND bls.target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
      AND bls.target_table_name = '$$target_table_name'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
			AND target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
            AND target_table_name = '$$target_table_name'
      )
)
select distinct 
bronze_dr.originating_source_name,
bronze_dr.originating_load_type,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_md5checksum,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_effective_start_datetime,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_effective_end_datetime,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_status,
bronze_dr.system_id as source_system_system_id,
bronze_dr.parent_id as source_system_parent_id,
bronze_dr.cmm_container as predictive_analytics_data_report_type,
bronze_dr.id as predictive_analytics_data_report_row_source_system_key,
bronze_dr.update_count as source_system_update_count,
bronze_dr.update_user as source_system_update_user,
bronze_dr.update_timestamp as source_system_update_timestamp,
bronze_dr.template_id_ref as data_report_template_id_reference,
bronze_dr.type_cd as data_report_type_code,
bronze_dr.source_cd as data_report_source_code,
bronze_dr.status_cd as data_report_status_code,
bronze_dr.result_cd as data_report_result_code,
bronze_dr.request_type_cd as request_type_code,
bronze_dr.transmitted_dt as data_report_transmitted_date,
bronze_dr.transmitted_tm as data_report_transmitted_time,
bronze_dr.received_dt as data_report_received_date,
bronze_dr.received_tm as data_report_received_time,
bronze_dr.processed_dt as data_report_processed_date,
bronze_dr.processed_tm as data_report_processed_time,
bronze_dr.add_dt as data_report_add_date,
bronze_dr.add_tm as data_report_add_time,
bronze_dr.party_id as party_id,
bronze_dr.row_id as source_system_row_id,
bronze_dr.state_specific_code as state_specific_code,
bronze_dr.inspection_number as inspection_number,
bronze_dr.inspection_id as inspection_id,
cb.batch_id AS batch_id,
silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_id,
silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_row_md5checksum
FROM $$staging_schema.acx_data_report bronze_dr
LEFT JOIN $$refined_schema.predictive_analytics_data_report silver_dr
    ON COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_dr.id), '') = COALESCE(CAST(silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_row_source_system_key AS VARCHAR), '')
   AND CAST(TRIM(bronze_dr.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(silver_dr.source_system_system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_dr.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_type, '')
   AND silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND silver_dr.predictive_analytics_data_report_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    bronze_dr.system_id,
    bronze_dr.cmm_container,
    bronze_dr.id;

fields.name: o_source_system_update_timestamp
fields.expression:
IIF(
    ISNULL(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP) 
    OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP))) = 0,
    SYSDATE,
    IIF(
        INSTR(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP, '.') > 0,
        TO_DATE(
            SUBSTR(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP, 1, INSTR(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP, '.') - 1) || 
            SUBSTR(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP, LENGTH(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP)-2, 3),
            'MM/DD/YYYY HH:MI:SS AM'
        ),
        TO_DATE(SOURCE_SYSTEM_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP, 'MM/DD/YYYY')
    )
)
